{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Overview</h2>Wish of Hers takes place within the dreamworld of the protagonist, where reality bends and shifts with every step. As you navigate through these surreal landscapes, you uncover that someone is manipulating your dreams, guiding you towards a deeper purpose. Each battle you face brings you closer to the truth, as you gather strength and abilities to confront the ultimate enemy lurking within your dreams.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Abilities</h2>Purchase <strong>Power Cards</strong> to gain unique and powerful abilities, each tailored to enhance your combat strategy. These abilities range from devastating attacks to defensive maneuvers and can be combined in creative ways to adapt to the ever-changing challenges of the dreamworld.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/extras/Description_Purchase_Abilities.png?t=1725423110\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Upgrades</h2>Use the <strong>Reality Shaper</strong> to upgrade your abilities, allowing them to evolve and become even more potent. With each upgrade, your abilities gain new effects and increased power, giving you the edge you need as you delve deeper into the mysteries of your dreams.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/extras/Description_Upgraded_Abilities.png?t=1725423110\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1725423110","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1725423110","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/142c95bbb5f356585cf31ddd4e542f7269499700/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1725423110","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/142c95bbb5f356585cf31ddd4e542f7269499700/capsule